Program: Discovery
Title: Living Together - ants
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrymp
Last Broadcast Date: 10 March 2004
How ants live together - the social skills of leaf cutter ants. When it comes to advanced societies ants come pretty close to top of the animal kingdom. How they manage to care for each other in a cohesive society has fascinated scientists. What can we learn from them?